@node Most recent bibliography file
@section Most recent bibliography file

@vindex zotra-extras-most-recent-bibfile
The variable @code{zotra-extras-most-recent-bibfile} holds the path of the bibliography file used by the most recently added entry. It is set by @code{zotra-extras-add-entry} (@ref{Adding entries}) when the user selects a bibliography file, and is read by @code{zotra-extras-open-in-ebib} (@ref{Ebib post-processing}) to switch to the correct @samp{ebib} database. The initial value is @code{nil}.

@node Most recent bibliography key
@section Most recent bibliography key

@vindex zotra-extras-most-recent-bibkey
The variable @code{zotra-extras-most-recent-bibkey} holds the Bib@TeX{} key of the most recently added entry. It is set by @code{zotra-extras-after-add-process-bibtex} (@ref{Bib@TeX{} cleanup}) after cleanup processing, and is read by the entry-opening workflow to navigate to the correct entry in @samp{ebib}. The initial value is @code{nil}.

@node Default URL list file
@section Default URL list file

@vindex zotra-extras-add-multiple-urls-from-file
The constant @code{zotra-extras-add-multiple-urls-from-file} (the variable, not the command of the same name) holds the default file path for the URL list used by the command @code{zotra-extras-add-multiple-urls-from-file} (@ref{Batch processing}). Its value is @samp{zotra-add-multiple-urls.txt} in the downloads directory (@code{paths-dir-downloads}).

